Q18: I used R. See code below. /  / setwd("D:/Downloads") /  / data <- read.csv("ML3StroopData.csv",header=TRUE) /  / sample <- sample(1:nrow(data),25,replace=FALSE) /  / data_s <- data[sample,] /  / MC <- MI <- S1 <- S2 <- numeric() /  / for(i in 1:nrow(data_s)){ /    /   MC[i] <- rnorm(1,mean(data_s$MC[i]-15,sd=20)) /   MI[i] <- rnorm(1,mean(data_s$MI[i]+15,sd=20)) /    /   S1[i] <- rnorm(1,mean=data_s$S[i],sd=20) /   S2[i] <- rnorm(1,mean=data_s$S[i],sd=20) /    / } /  /  / t.test(MC,MI) / t.test(S1,S2) /  /  / writeClipboard(as.character(round(MC,3))) / writeClipboard(as.character(round(S1,3))) / writeClipboard(as.character(round(MI,3))) / writeClipboard(as.character(round(S2,3))) /
